## âœ… Minimal Compile Command (42-style)

```bash
gcc -Wall -Wextra -Werror main.c
```

### What the flags mean:

| Flag      | Meaning                     |
| --------- | --------------------------- |
| `-Wall`   | Enable most common warnings |
| `-Wextra` | Enable even more warnings   |
| `-Werror` | Treat warnings as errors    |

